{"name":"Kudough","permalink":"kudough","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/kudough","homepage_url":"http://www.kudough.com","blog_url":"http://kudough.com/resources/blog","blog_feed_url":"","twitter_username":"kudough","category_code":"enterprise","number_of_employees":2,"founded_year":2010,"founded_month":8,"founded_day":null,"deadpooled_year":null,"deadpooled_month":null,"deadpooled_day":null,"deadpooled_url":null,"tag_list":"employee-recognition, employee-motivation, employee-incentives, employee-rewards","alias_list":null,"email_address":"info@kudough.com","phone_number":"888.583.6844","description":"Web Based Employee Recognition","created_at":"Thu Feb 23 16:21:55 UTC 2012","updated_at":"Tue Oct 02 19:42:58 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Kudough is a web based employee recognition and reward solution for organizations of any size.</p>\n\n<p>If you have employees, then you need Kudough. Employees are your greatest asset, we’re sure you’ve heard this phrase time and time again. But here at Kudough we really mean it.</p>\n\n<p>Ask yourself, without your fantastic employees where would your organization be? Would your organization be as successful as it is today? Of course not. Your employees are like a garden that needs to be cared for, nurtured and watered regularly. Your employees have the on-going need to know that what they do for you for one third of their day has meaning and value. And that doesn’t mean just a paycheck every two weeks. Your employees need on-going praise and recognition for their daily efforts that help your business remain successful.</p>\n\n<p>Kudough makes employee recognition and rewards simple.</p>\n\n<p>Kudough delivers the leading cloud-based employee rewards and recognition solution. Loved by organizations of all sizes for its feature rich simplicity and cost effectiveness.</p>\n\n<p>Our Solution</p>\n\n<p>Kudough makes it easy to recognize your workforce from any computer with an Internet connection. When an employee does something remarkable, simply log in, click on the person&#8217;s name and send some Kudough love their way.</p>\n\n<p>Closed a big sale? BAM! Kudough.</p>\n\n<p>Avoided a potential overbilling to a customer? BAM! Kudough.</p>\n\n<p>Just celebrated 5 years with your organization? BAM! Kudough.</p>\n\n<p>Cleaned up a spill in the lunchroom avoiding an accident? BAM! Kudough.</p>\n\n<p>You get the idea.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,37],"assets/images/resized/0017/5609/175609v2-max-150x150.png"],[[250,62],"assets/images/resized/0017/5609/175609v2-max-250x250.png"],[[450,113],"assets/images/resized/0017/5609/175609v2-max-450x450.png"]],"attribution":null},"products":[],"relationships":[{"is_past":false,"title":"CEO","person":{"first_name":"Jason","last_name":"Johnson","permalink":"jason-johnson-2","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"CTO","person":{"first_name":"Jeff","last_name":"Madison","permalink":"jeff-madison","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Advisor","person":{"first_name":"Alan","last_name":"Wizemann","permalink":"alan-wizemann","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Advisor","person":{"first_name":"Colleen","last_name":"Sexton","permalink":"colleen-sexton","image":null}},{"is_past":true,"title":"CFO","person":{"first_name":"John","last_name":"Grant","permalink":"john-grant","image":null}}],"competitions":[],"providerships":[{"title":"Cloud Based Application Hosting","is_past":false,"provider":{"name":"Microsoft Azure","permalink":"microsoft-azure","image":null}},{"title":"IAAS","is_past":false,"provider":{"name":"SoftLayer","permalink":"softlayer-2","image":null}},{"title":"Pivotal Tracker","is_past":false,"provider":{"name":"Pivotal Labs Inc.","permalink":"pivotal-labs-inc","image":null}},{"title":"Mail Transport","is_past":false,"provider":{"name":"Sendgrid","permalink":"sendgrid-2","image":null}},{"title":"User Support and Helpdesk","is_past":false,"provider":{"name":"Zendesk","permalink":"zendesk-3","image":null}},{"title":"Web Traff